# Updating Seshy?

## Here's what you should know.

<%= partial 'download-button' %>

For a smooth upgrade:

1. Make sure to quit Seshy
1. Download the dmg installer file containing the app
1. Open your 'Downloads' folder in Finder
1. Double click the installer to start it
1. Drag the Seshy icon into your 'Applications' folder
1. Click the "Replace" button in the confirmation that pops up
1. Double click the 'Applications' folder to open it
1. In the 'Applications' folder window, double click on Seshy to open it

[Check out the changelog to see what's changed.](/changelog/)
